{"type":"message","id":"3a75b963","parentId":"5348a5b2","timestamp":"2026-03-29T18:00:02.912Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:0bb637bb-765d-4c8a-b721-260619faf16f Tobias Task Watchdog] Run the Tobias task watchdog. Read C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog\\README.md for context. Execute python C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog\\watchdog.py, inspect its JSON output, and follow this rule strictly: if notifications is empty, reply with exactly NO_REPLY and nothing else. If there are notifications, rewrite each one in clean human Portuguese, concise but informative, and deliver them. Do not send silent confirmations. Do not explain empty scans. Do not invent status.\nCurrent time: Sunday, March 29th, 2026 — 15:00 (America/Sao_Paulo) / 2026-03-29 18:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1774807202830}}
{"type":"message","id":"d453f5aa","parentId":"3a75b963","timestamp":"2026-03-29T18:00:05.731Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job asking me to:\n1. Read the README for context about a task watchdog\n2. Execute a Python script that outputs JSON\n3. If notifications are empty, reply with exactly \"NO_REPLY\" and nothing else\n4. If there are notifications, rewrite them in Portuguese and deliver them\n5. Don't send silent confirmations or explain empty scans\n\nLet me start by reading the README to understand what this watchdog does.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_012VFNhvS9ig5PPJbd7cJTM4","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog\\README.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-haiku-4-5","usage":{"input":10,"output":179,"cacheRead":15639,"cacheWrite":740,"totalTokens":16568,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0008950000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0015639000000000002,"cacheWrite":0.000925,"total":0.0033939000000000005}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774807202997,"responseId":"msg_01WuZTtwC1K5fzM9E4RnetvJ"}}
{"type":"message","id":"74d7765a","parentId":"d453f5aa","timestamp":"2026-03-29T18:00:06.085Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_012VFNhvS9ig5PPJbd7cJTM4","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Task Watchdog\n\nGlobal task registry + watchdog for Tobias long-running tasks.\n\n## Goal\n- track tasks launched by Tobias\n- check every 5 minutes\n- notify Lucca every 10 minutes while running\n- send final notification on completion/failure\n- stay silent when no tasks are active\n\n## Files\n- `config.json` — watchdog settings\n- `active_tasks.json` — active monitored tasks\n- `task_history.jsonl` — completed/failed task history\n- `watchdog.py` — deterministic status checker\n\n## Scope (MVP)\n- monitors Tobias-launched subagents first\n- stores global registry so it can work across chats/surfaces\n- internal timestamps are ISO; user-facing messages must be human formatted\n\n## Operational protocol (mandatory)\nFor every long-running subagent launched by Tobias:\n1. spawn the subagent\n2. immediately register it in `active_tasks.json`\n3. only after registration, confirm to Lucca that the task was launched\n\nRule:\n- spawn without register = incomplete launch\n- do not claim a task is being monitored unless it is already in the registry\n\n## Safety layers\nThe watchdog design uses three layers together:\n1. **Launch wrapper discipline** — spawn -> register -> confirm\n2. **No-confirmation-without-registry** — Tobias must not claim monitoring without persisted registration\n3. **Launch audit** — `watchdog_launch_audit.py` scans for recent unregistered subagent sessions and auto-registers them as a fallback safety net\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774807206084}}
{"type":"message","id":"4baaad84","parentId":"74d7765a","timestamp":"2026-03-29T18:00:07.564Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now executing the watchdog:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01PxStHajcP7GtKFPBGtaQDR","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog\\watchdog.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-haiku-4-5","usage":{"input":6,"output":81,"cacheRead":15639,"cacheWrite":1011,"totalTokens":16737,"cost":{"input":0.000006,"output":0.00040500000000000003,"cacheRead":0.0015639000000000002,"cacheWrite":0.0012637500000000001,"total":0.0032386500000000005}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774807206086,"responseId":"msg_01WbX725gd5R3QHWtGkaWoZw"}}
